trans-unit.source: Gets the <xref href="System.Printing.PrintTicket"></xref>, if a ticket exists, that is associated with the <xref href="System.Windows.Documents.FixedPage"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar den <xref href="System.Printing.PrintTicket"> </xref>, om det finns för en biljett, som är associerad med den <xref href="System.Windows.Documents.FixedPage"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: For more information about the <xref:System.Printing.PrintTicket> part of an [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_xps](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-xps-md.md)] page, see chapter 2 in the [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xps](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] specification, which you can obtain at [XPS: Specification and License Downloads](http://www.microsoft.com/whdc/xps/downloads.mspx).
trans-unit.target: Mer information om den <xref:System.Printing.PrintTicket>ingår i en [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_xps](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-xps-md.md)] sidan, finns i kapitlet 2 i den [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xps](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] -specifikationen som du kan hämta på [XPS: specifikation och licens hämtar](http://www.microsoft.com/whdc/xps/downloads.mspx).</xref:System.Printing.PrintTicket>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Printing.PrintTicket"></xref> that contains the default printing options for the page; or <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""></xref> if no <xref href="System.Printing.PrintTicket"></xref> exists for the page.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Printing.PrintTicket"> </xref> som innehåller standard utskriftsalternativ för sidan, eller <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""> </xref> om inget <xref href="System.Printing.PrintTicket"> </xref> finns på sidan.
